        <span class="eng">Eng. Luciano Mori</span>
        Cloud, AI <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Security<br/>built to scale.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">
        Sr. DevOps Engineer shipping <span class="glow">cost-efficient AI workflows</span> on secure cloud infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Architecting and deploying production AI agents, hardened CI/CD, and IaC across AWS, Azure &amp; GCP. Shipped, monitored, and built to last.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucianosmori/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
